<h1>Upcoming activities at St. Paul's</h1>

<h2>Men's Group</h2>
<p> Friday fellowship  meetings of the men of the parish begin at 7:30 a.m. in season (October to May). This informal group under the guidance of Fr. Frank welcomes all men of St. Paul's to break bread (pastries) and share some good conversations.  The first Friday of each month we share Eucharist before getting down to conversations.  Suggestions of speakers are welcome.   It is a cordial group that would like to include you!</p>
