 <h2>Art Hale Movie Night</h2> 
<%= image_tag("https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/saintpaulsnaplesorg/logos/filmStrip.jpg", class: "floatleft", width: "110") %>

  <p><b>Movie Night </b>is the second Tuesday of the month, 6:30 p.m. in the library, during season (October to May). Typically, we watch a film and discuss its messages and implications.  </p>
